name: SXZ Lady Jaina Proudmoore
description:
Inspired by great job of Master Corneo.
Not so perfect as his, but i tried.
So feel free to use and share your review in section down below.

Trained on NAI with clip skip 2, so it should work pretty fine with any anime-based model.

You also may use slight adjustments in prompt like adult, lady, big breasts, white corset, white hair, single braid, armored pauldrons to increase strength of embedding.

Also this negative prompt may be helpful twin braids, pointy ears, elf, loli
